request.doc:
Pass the new file contents as JSON:

PUT https://{appliance_hostname}/wga/user_map_cdas/{usermap_file_id}

PUT_DATA: {"content":"user_map_cdas_file_content"}

Pass the new file contents as a file:

PUT https://{appliance_hostname}/wga/user_map_cdas/{usermap_file_id}

PUT_DATA: { "file":"user_map_cdas_file" }
